Subject: Re: [T2] re- [T2] My steering has alot of play....advice needed

Don't forget to check out the rubber bushings on your rear torsion arms. 
Easy to replace the outer units. 10-15 minutes each provided that the cover 
screws come out easy. Inner bushing replacement requires torsion arm 
removal.

Worn out bushings create road wander.

Chris 
